# baseURL
@baseURL = http://localhost:3000

###
# Create a new diary
POST {{ baseURL }}/diaries
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "今天是一个美好的日子，我感到非常开心和满足。早上起床后阳光明媚，让我的心情也变得很好。工作上也进展顺利，完成了几个重要的任务。晚上和朋友聊天，分享了彼此的近况，感觉很温暖。"
}

###
# Get all diaries
GET {{ baseURL }}/diaries

###
# Get diary by ID
GET {{ baseURL }}/diaries/1

###
# Delete diary by ID
DELETE {{ baseURL }}/diaries/1

###
# Analyze diary content
POST {{ baseURL }}/diaries/1/analyze

###
# Get diary analysis
GET {{ baseURL }}/diaries/1/analysis

